text: Barneveld is a hamlet (and census-designated place) located within the Town of Trenton in Oneida County, New York, United States. The population was 272 at the 2020 census. Barneveld is located at (43.274087, -75.188710). ==References== Category:Census-designated places in New York (state) Category:Hamlets in New York (state)
title: Barneveld, New York
